{"id":2296,"date":"2024-11-28T19:59:28","date_gmt":"2024-11-28T19:59:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2296"},"modified":"2024-12-01T03:18:08","modified_gmt":"2024-12-01T03:18:08","slug":"hard-stone-gem-trader","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/hard-stone-gem-trader\/","title":{"rendered":"Hard Stone to Gem Trader (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left widesecond\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Gurun Town<\/strong> &#8211; Inside of the house directly behind the Gurun Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Gives the player any type of Gem in exchange for Hard Stones<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Hard Stones<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>20 Hard Stones<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Gurun Town Pokemon Center and follow the brown path going north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-gurun-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Gurun Town Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Gurun Town Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter the house northwest of the Regi Statue.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-house-northeast-of-the-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the house northeast of the Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the house northeast of the Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Hard Stone to Gem trader is the mountain climber NPC inside the house sitting at the table.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-hard-stone-to-gem-npc.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Hard Stone to Gem NPC. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Hard Stone to Gem NPC.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-gem-npc-asking-for-hard-stones.jpg\" alt=\"The Gem NPC asking for Hard Stones. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Gem NPC asking for Hard Stones.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You can go to this NPC to acquire <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/items\/gems\/\">any type of Gem<\/a> in exchange for 20 Hard Stones. However, you must first complete the mission <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-010\/\">\u201cAs Hard as They Come\u201d<\/a> before this NPC will trade with you.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2297,"parent":2143,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-2296","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbn